Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.28,Ending_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HF7EABE&}So close
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:31.81,Ending_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HF7EABE&}But far away, so far I can't touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:33.27,Ending_English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&H81EBF7&}I'll hold on
